---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Zro2One">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 prose prose-slate">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> March 2026</p>
    <p>Zro2One is built to help people learn AI. We collect as little data as possible.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Email address (only if you subscribe to the newsletter)</li>
      <li>Basic anonymous analytics (page views, referrers)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Send newsletter updates you explicitly subscribed to</li>
      <li>Understand which content is useful so we can improve the site</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we do not do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No selling personal data</li>
      <li>No invasive ad tracking</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>We use Buttondown for newsletter delivery and Vercel for hosting/analytics.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions: hello@zro2.one</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
